A TCP server that writes data to the file "MyServFile.tmp" (if the file does not exist, it is created).

The server writes to the system log (/var/log/syslog) process name "mytcpserv" and information about:
receiving the SIGTERM and SIGHUP signals,
socket creation error,
socket binding error,
accept socket connection failed,
receive data failed,
closing socket connection,
record file creation error

Server port: 8080
